    Set up simulation stuff for biologicals

    Setup_Sim_Biologicals.Rd

    Set up simulation stuff for biologicals

    Setup_Sim_Biologicals(
  n_sims = n_sims,
  n_yrs = n_yrs,
  n_regions = n_regions,
  n_ages = n_ages,
  n_sexes = n_sexes,
  base_M_value,
  M_pattern,
  base_WAA_values,
  WAA_pattern,
  base_Maturity_AA_values,
  Maturity_AA_pattern
)

    Arguments

    n_sims

    Number of simulations

    n_yrs

    Number of years

    n_regions

    Number of regions

    n_ages

    Number of ages

    n_sexes

    Number of sexes

    base_M_value

    Base natural mortality value dimensioned by regions, ages, sexes

    M_pattern

    Natural mortality pattern. Options include: constant

    base_WAA_values

    Base weight-at-age values dimensioned by regions, ages, sexes

    WAA_pattern

    Weight-at-age pattern. Options include: constant

    base_Maturity_AA_values

    Base maturity values dimensioned by regions, ages, sexes

    Maturity_AA_pattern

    Maturity pattern. Options include: constant
